{"tid":212274,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"估唔到我都有睇TVB劇喊既一日...","createTime":"2017-04-22T10:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T15:50:58.000Z","uid":77287,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f78fed065ef553290871b2e1a6bf4fb83e1463d","tid":212274,"uid":77287,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:10:48.000Z","msg":"前幾日睇番天與地，首播係2011，話好突破，尾段音樂會一場叫人上街，只係當時感覺不大，覺得好炒作<br />\n<br />\n經過依幾年發生既事，對依個地方好多野好灰心<br />\n<br />\n聽到林保怡同劉丹講，以前自己堅持既野係一啲用都無，已經眼濕濕<br />\n<br />\n直至音樂會一段，睇番，就好似預言咁，諗番大家喺旺角金鐘流過血汗同眼淚，啲回憶番晒黎，忍唔住喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa3c96637510d1c3674b79b756fbca63de584f28","tid":212274,"uid":77287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:11:51.000Z","msg":"仲有無啲戲/劇，係後來現實發生既事，賦予另一重意義，突然令你覺得震撼或者感動？"},{"pid":"b0ea9a8e2d207b13d793964207cdbbb69cfb7bca","tid":212274,"uid":44775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T12:38:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有無啲戲/劇，係後來現實發生既事，賦予另一重意義，突然令你覺得震撼或者感動？</blockquote><br />\n十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a1202cdac9e13f4034c70b4ff877340fef9449","tid":212274,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T12:52:59.000Z","msg":"表姐，妳好嘢"},{"pid":"f5b9ebe1ecd4b0b0ed5fd5fe3bfe0acf3d75ad9c","tid":212274,"uid":2386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T12:53:34.000Z","msg":"個平行時空結局真係喊咗出嚟"},{"pid":"60ee6be88202478cf72ce64dd47458d98684f4e6","tid":212274,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T14:44:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個平行時空結局真係喊咗出嚟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實結他頭個幾個音一起已經打動到我起雞皮"},{"pid":"6747a835cf875fba2b40be31f9272102bdcac225","tid":212274,"uid":77287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T16:58:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有無啲戲/劇，係後來現實發生既事，賦予另一重意義，突然令你覺得震撼或者感動？</blockquote><br />\n十年<img src=\"/assets/fac